content: "[[html]]
<style type="text/css">
@import url(http://scp-jp.wdfiles.com/local--files/japanese-syntax/scp-WikidotCss.css);
</style>
<style>
.form-table > tbody > tr:nth-child(odd) {
    background: #fff0f0;
}
.form-labels {
    vertical-align: top;
}
.form-table .form-message {
    color: red;
    font-weight: bold;
}
.form-table > tbody > tr:last-child {
    opacity: 0.5;
    transition: opacity 0.25s ease;
}
.form-table > tbody > tr:last-child:hover {
    opacity: 1;
}
</style>
<script type="text/javascript" src="http://scp-jp.wdfiles.com/local--files/japanese-syntax/scpHTMLblockCtrl_ver1_ex.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript">
isHTMLblockHide = true;
</script>
<div id="action-area" style="display: block;">
<div>
<table class="form-table">
<tbody>
<tr class="form-row row-1">
<td class="form-labels">
<span class="form-label"></span>
</td>
<td class="form-values"><div class="form-value field-content"> <textarea cols="40" rows="10" name="field-content" placeholder="" class="form-control form-wiki">**説明:** 保存不可能なAnomalousオブジェクトの報告書
**回収日:** 20██/██/██
**回収場所:** 財団データベース
**現状:** 編集状態を維持してデータベースに登録。
**追記:** これ、本当に異常性なんですか？データベースの不具合とかではなく。 -██研究員</textarea> <span class="form-message text-danger"></span></div></td>
</tr>
<tr class="form-row row-2">
<td class="form-labels">
<span class="form-label">移転用</span>
</td>
<td class="form-values"><span class="form-value field-tf2"> <label class="radio-inline"><input name="field-tf2" type="radio" class="form-select" value="0" checked="checked">使用しない</label><label class="radio-inline"><input name="field-tf2" type="radio" class="form-select" value="1">使用する</label> <span class="form-message text-danger"></span></span><span class="form-value field-author"> <input type="text" size="40" name="field-author" value="" placeholder="※許可無く使用しないでください" class="form-control form-text"> <span class="form-message text-danger"></span></span></td>
</tr>
</tbody></table>
<div id="edit-page-captcha">
</div>
<div class="buttons alignleft">
<input type="button" name="cancel" id="edit-cancel-button" value="キャンセル" onclick="WIKIDOT.modules.PageEditModule.listeners.cancel(event)">
<input type="button" name="save" id="edit-save-button" value="保存" onclick="WIKIDOT.modules.PageEditModule.listeners.save(event)" class="">
</div>
</form>
<div id="background-file-upload" style="display: none;"></div>
</div>
<div id="view-diff-div"></div>
</div>
<div id="scpHTMLblockResizeSwitch"></div>
[[/html]]"
tf2: '0'
author: ''
